==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: iodinated
<hw>iodinated</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>treated or
reacted with iodine; treated so as to combine with iodine.</def>
<note>The iodinating agent may be other than iodine itself, such as
compounds with active iodine.</note>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> iodized.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

